th: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica,Arial,STHeiTi,sans-serif&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190910/abbf590f5d7b40a39b882608b4cf809b.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px none; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 20px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica,Arial,STHeiTi,sans-serif&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">动力方面，新车将继续搭载硬顶版同款的6.2L V8发动机，最大功率或为502马力，峰值扭矩637牛·米，传动匹配全新的8速双离合变速箱。目前新车的0-100km/h加速时间尚未公布，但其车重数据为1650kg。</p><p><br/></p>');
INSERT INTO `jc_content_txt` VALUES (728, 2579, 'content', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">中国银保监会日前通报，2019年上半年，银保监会及其派出机构共接收涉及保险公司的保险消费投诉48194件，同比增长0.61%。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.img.cctvpic.com/photoworkspace/contentimg/2019/09/10/2019091010203482948.jpg\" alt=\" \"/></p><p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">数据显示，上半年，银保监会及其派出机构接收并转保险公司处理的保险合同纠纷投诉46911件，同比增长0.03%，占投诉总量的97.34%；涉嫌违法违规投诉1283件，同比增长27.79%，占投诉总量的2.66%。而投诉涉及的主要问题是理赔纠纷和销售纠纷。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `jc_content_txt` VALUES (729, 2311, 'content', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 美国德克萨斯州总检察长肯·帕克斯顿9日宣布，来自美国48个州、哥伦比亚特区以及海外属地波多黎各的50名总检察长正式对美国互联网科技巨头谷歌公司发起反垄断调查。</span><br/></p><p class=\"photo_img_20190808\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/1.75em Arial, 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p1.img.cctvpic.com/photoworkspace/contentimg/2019/09/10/2019091011022037752.jpg\" alt=\" \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" width=\"500\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/1.75em Arial, 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 近来，美国多家大型互联网技术企业因滥用市场影响力，侵犯用户隐私权而被推上风口浪尖，其中谷歌公司被指利用其搜索引擎引导用户购买商品，存在反竞争行为，同时其网页上还存在有虚假新闻。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/1.75em Arial, 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 此次调查将重点关注谷歌是否已经损害了竞争者和消费者的利益，调查人员还将对谷歌在搜索广告和其他业务方面展开调查。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/1.75em Arial, 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这次对谷歌的调查由德克萨斯州总检察长牵头，在全美50个州中，只有亚拉巴马州和加利福尼亚州的总检察长没有参与这一调查。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/1.75em Arial, 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 近来，美国多个监管机构频频对硅谷互联网企业势力过大表示担忧，并对其获得大量专利数据的提出质疑，认为这将使得这些巨头吞并其他竞争对手，保持垄断地位，损害消费者利益。本月6日，以纽约州为代表的多州就已针对互联网企业脸书发起反垄断调查。</p><p><br/></p>');
INSERT INTO `jc_content_txt` VALUES (738, 2332, 'content', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">北京时间9月10日，2020欧洲杯预选赛I组一场焦点战展开争夺，比利时客场4比0大胜苏格兰，卢卡库传射，维尔马伦和阿尔德韦雷尔德先后破门，德布劳内上演助攻帽子戏法后进球。比利时6战全胜领跑。</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-size-adjust: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这是双方第20次交手，此前比利时12胜3平4负占据上风。比利时近5战苏格兰取得全胜并保持零封。苏格兰上次取胜比利时还是1987年。卢卡库、查德利、默尔滕斯和登东克尔轮换出场。</p><p style=\"text-size-adjust: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　比利时第9分钟领先，默尔滕斯反击中直传，德布劳内突破至禁区边缘无私横传，跟进的卢卡库12码处低射破门。第24分钟，比利时战术角球配合险些失误，德布劳内右路传中，维尔马伦小禁区边缘捅射入网，2-0。</p><p style=\"text-size-adjust: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　第32分钟，德布劳内开出角球，阿尔德韦雷尔德10码处头球攻门击中横梁下沿弹过门线，3-0。第82分钟，卢卡库斜传，德布劳内禁区左侧12码处射入远角，4-0。</p><p><br/></p>');
INSERT INTO `jc_content_txt` VALUES (739, 2577, 'content', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">北京时间9月9日，篮球世界杯复赛K组最后一场，老迈的巴西队没能给美国队制造太多麻烦，美国队89-73轻松取胜巴西队。美国队5战全胜获得小组头名，携手捷克队晋级8强并直通东京奥运会，巴西队出局。四分之一决赛，美国队将迎战法国队。每节比分：21-18、22-21、24-17、22-17（美国队在前）。</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-size-adjust: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"/u/cms/www/201909/10141953xjau.jpg\" style=\"max-width:750px\"/></p><p style=\"text-size-adjust: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">技术统计：</p><p style=\"text-size-adjust: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　美国队，沃克16分5助攻、特纳16分8篮板、巴恩斯10分、布朗11分4篮板4助攻、斯马特9分、米德尔顿9分6篮板、米切尔6分6篮板7助攻。</p><p style=\"text-size-adjust: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　巴西队，本尼特21分、瓦莱乔14分8篮板3助攻、巴博萨14分、胡尔塔斯7分4篮板5助攻。</p><p><br/></p>');
INSERT INTO `jc_content_txt` VALUES (745, 2925, 'content', '<span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Menlo, monospace; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none; font-size: 14px;\"> 首先：准备一个大光圈镜头，最好是中长焦焦段。如2.0或者1.4等光圈；或者85焦段以上的中长焦镜头，来拍摄猫的特写，突出喵星人的神态特点，虚化背景，可以有效的和背景分离出来，突出主体。</span>');
INSERT INTO `jc_content_txt` VALUES (749, 2612, 'content', '<p>&nbsp; 1.360安全卫士是一款由奇虎360公司推出的功能强、效果好、受用户欢迎的安全杀毒软件<br/>&nbsp; 2.目前4.2亿中国网民中，首选安装360的已超过3亿<br/>&nbsp; 3.拥有查杀木马、清理插件、修复漏洞、电脑体检、电脑救援、保护隐私，电脑专家，清理垃圾，清理痕迹多种功能<br/>&nbsp; 4.独创了&amp;ldquo;木马防火墙&quot;&amp;ldquo;360密盘&amp;rdquo;等功能<br/>&nbsp; 5.依靠抢先侦测和云端鉴别，可全面、智能地拦截各类木马，保护用户的帐号、隐私等重要信息<br/>&nbsp; 6.内含的360软件管家还可帮助用户轻松下载、升级和强力卸载各种应用软件</p>');
